Package: scStudio
Title: Interactive Local Single-Cell RNA-seq Analysis Studio
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("scStudio", "Authors", email = "noreply@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A localhost-first, browser-based interactive application for
    single-cell RNA-seq analysis. Users launch the app with a single command,
    upload a count matrix (Seurat/SingleCellExperiment .rds, 10x, .h5, or a
    plain table), and interactively run a modern analysis pipeline -- quality
    control, doublet removal, normalization, dimensionality reduction, batch
    integration, clustering, non-linear embedding, marker detection, and
    cell-type annotation -- entirely on their own machine. Every step offers
    method alternatives, adjustable thresholds, a beginner-friendly explanation,
    a result summary, an interactive preview plot with hover details, and
    reproducible parameter logging.
